которые нешаблонно мыслят растёт эта сфера даёт возможность применить художественные технические навыки влиять качество востребованность товаров какие профессии востребованы диджитале получить навыки community don ’ t miss danilo woznica ’ s post and comment if you ’ d like us to add a specific theme changelog — yes we know… summer took over the northern hemisphere and most of you are out for some relaxing holidays—or at least we hope so when you are back go over the full july changelog to see what we implemented this past month it ’ s 100 worth the read want more 📰️ as we mentioned at the beginning this is just the product section of our community newsletter which contains some events community spotlights and resources if you want to receive the full version instead subscribe ✨ we enjoy seeing what you build using codesandbox so do share with us what you ’ re working on or which insights you would like to hear from us thank you for using codesandbox and stay tuned for the next спам 1 категория 0 тема inside the box september product update codesandbox hellocodesandboxio дата 06102023 1720 кому sekerbek8gmailcom replyto hellocodesandboxio inside the box september product update ai commit messages 20 vs codepowered command palette streaming search results and more ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ inside the box september product update aloha 👋 another month bites the dust admit it you read that singing didnt you it is time to unroll another edition of our newsletter latest product news new command palette powered by vs code 🔥 — we overhauled our command palette and file picker to use its vs code equivalent this has lots of benefits and the palette should now feel much faster and more reliable plus when you run commands like ask boxy run task or create branch that will activate a new quick picker ai commit messages 20 — one of the most loved boxy ai features has definitely been the aigenerated commit messages isnt it wonderful not having to write every commit by hand in version 20 boxy now generates a commit title and description to give even more context to your changes also when you open a pr it will be prefilled with a short title and description based on the commits streaming search results — searching the entire codebase can be very resourceintensive on larger projects so we have improved the search logic to use the new pitcher client and use streaming whenever possible searching should now feel instant full changelog — there are a few more things we freshly backed not cookies so be sure to check the changelog for all the goodies we shipped 🚀 want more 📰️ this update only includes the product updates section of our community calendar any good songs about it till we find one lets see what kept us busy at codesandbox this last month latest product news dev container support 📦 — in one of our biggest product releases of 2023 we introduced dev container spec in codesandbox this is now the default spec for all codesandbox projects and you can use our brandnew devtool to configure any environment in seconds 🔥 plus with the latest update to our vs code extension you can now connect to containers running inside the codesandbox microvms using the dev containers extension this brings improved support for repos and sandboxes configured with dev containers and gets rid of the vs code trust modal codesandbox enterprise 🏦 — we introduced codesandbox enterprise as a new offering that brings scalability availability security and trust to our cde—the only one in the market that spins up an environment in 15 seconds is available 247 and is fully collaborative private beta now open boxy ai gets gpt4 🤖 — we have upgraded boxy your codesandbox ai assistant to use gpt4 by default based on our testing this as expected greatly increases the quality of boxys responses boxy is available to pro subscribers full changelog — this past month we made a lot of improvements and fixes across the board but we also shipped some powerful new features check the changelog page for all the details on what we shipped 🚀 want more 📰️ this
